edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n如果林鄭有一日走出嚟答應五大訴求<br />\n我嗰刻反而唔知點算<br />\n而家佢態度強硬 咪大家一齊死囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db92cc6411b17d649b56acf847660d079ed03cd0","tid":1490551,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"將軍澳斬傷女子為信報記者 本報譴責暴力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225282/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2225282%2F&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=aa3b89ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225282/</a>"},{"pid":"f8cc8b5f4af0009bb44cb39555483853353df3f4","tid":1490551,"uid":293515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12292ba9b53640bd8da9ebca073441703a432008","tid":1490551,"uid":102700,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:51:10.000Z","msg":"自己記者俾人斬到入ICU仲係度出埋D咁野...信報..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"編文係前日寫，斬人係凌晨，信報截輸稿係午夜十二點。<br />\n<br />\n另外呢個唔係社評，係副刊政情散文。"}]}